data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home with open floor plan & hardwood floors throughout. As you step inside, you're greeted by the spacious living room, featuring a cozy fireplace, that seamlessly flows into the kitchen & breakfast room. The kitchen is equipped w/ stainless appliances, ample cabinet space, & large island that looks out over the primary level. A glass slider door leads you out to the expansive backyard with a brand new platform deck. The conveniently placed mud room & half bath complete the main floor. Upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, full bath that features custom cabinetry & 2nd floor laundry. The primary bedroom is a true oasis, boasting vaulted ceilings that create an airy atmosphere and a large walk-in closet. The ensuite bathroom features a soaking tub, double sink vanity & walk-in shower. The finished basement has a large bar area & bonus room, perfect for entertaining. Close to restaurants, shops, Greenway Bike Path & walking distance from the MetroLink!
